    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest" style="color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif">
      <span>Oldsmar, FL</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>CCC1337380</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>HappyRoof.com</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span style="color:#3B9FD9">(813) 595-7663</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHY SECTION -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Replace Your Roof in Oldsmar</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY OLDSMAR HOMEOWNERS CHOOSE HAPPY ROOF</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Oldsmar is a tight-knit community of roughly 15,000 residents nestled along the northern shore of Old Tampa Bay, straddling the border of Pinellas and Hillsborough counties. Happy Roof is proud to call Oldsmar home - our office is located at 141 Stevens Avenue, and many of our team members live in the surrounding area. When you hire us for a roof replacement in Oldsmar, you are hiring your neighbors.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">The city's housing stock ranges from the original homes near downtown Oldsmar and Race Track Road built in the 1960s and 1970s, to newer developments like Westwood Lakes and Tampa Bay Golf and Country Club that went up in the 1990s and 2000s. Roofs on the older homes are often on their second or third generation and showing significant wear - curling shingles, granule loss, and underlayment that has dried out after decades of Florida sun. Even the "newer" neighborhoods now have roofs approaching the 25-year mark where replacement becomes more practical than continued repairs.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Oldsmar's proximity to Old Tampa Bay means roofs in the waterfront areas off the Upper Tampa Bay Trail and near Mobbly Bay Preserve face elevated salt air exposure. Selecting the right material - and installing it correctly - is critical for long-term performance. Happy Roof holds Florida License #CCC1337380, handles all permitting, and backs every installation with an up to 15-year workmanship warranty. See our <a href="/oldsmar-roofing" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Oldsmar roofing page</a> for all services.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Architectural Shingles</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Owens Corning Duration HDZ rated for 130+ MPH winds. The most popular, cost-effective option for Oldsmar's inland and semi-coastal neighborhoods.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Standing Seam Metal</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Ideal for waterfront Oldsmar properties near Old Tampa Bay. Corrosion-resistant, heat-reflective, and built to last 40-60 years.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Concrete & Clay Tile</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Durable and attractive for Oldsmar homes with Mediterranean or Florida-style architecture. 50+ year lifespan with proper installation.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Up to 15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every Oldsmar roof replacement backed by our written up to 15-year workmanship warranty plus the manufacturer's material warranty.</p></div></div>
        </div>
