        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">County inspection for code compliance, then delivery of your up to 15-year workmanship warranty and manufacturer warranty documentation.</p>
